Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:08.69,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}果てしない空を往く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:12.14,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}見えない翼が導く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:15.67,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}遥か彼方、僕らを待つ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:21.06,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ見ぬ未来へと‥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:30.44,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Always　 醒めきってた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:33.61,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}速すぎる  Day and night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:36.73,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}透明な闇に囲まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:40.22,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も似た網の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:43.43,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Found you  あの日の風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:46.67,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揺れ動いたPassion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.10,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}And all of my past
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:53.09,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全てキミに会うためのProcessだったね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:56.04,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Slowly open up my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:58.66,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}within the blackness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:02.54,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼方から聞こえる予感に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:06.47,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}鼓動奮わせて居たいから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:10.32,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's unlimited  It's unlimited
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:13.82,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}If I can believe myself again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:17.16,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}光の中  目覚めていく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:20.88,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じてくれたキミとなら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.13,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:23.30,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never lose my way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:26.78,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここで生まれ変わる景色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:30.25,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傷さえいま誇りになる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:34.90,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だからキミと Burst The Gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------------OPCHNlrc----------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:08.69,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}去往不断延展的天边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:12.14,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}透明的翅膀将我引领
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:15.67,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}它在远方静待着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.77,0:02:21.06,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飞往未曾预见的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:30.44,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理智清醒时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:33.61,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}时常感到日夜流逝过快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:36.73,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}四周被透明的黑暗包围
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:40.22,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们都活在寸步难移的网中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:43.43,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寻觅你  每当风吹过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:46.67,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中激情仿佛随风跃动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:48.10,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}And all of my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:53.09,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一切皆为与你相会的前奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:56.04,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Slowly open up my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:58.66,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}within the blackness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:02.54,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}远方传来的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:06.47,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}让我不禁加快心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:10.32,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's unlimited  It's unlimited
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:13.82,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}If I can believe myself again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:17.16,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}光辉洒下  我逐渐苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:20.88,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要你我互信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.13,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:23.30,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never lose my way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:26.78,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眼前景色将焕然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:30.25,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}昔日伤痕亦成今日荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:34.90,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因此与你一起超越重力的束缚
